THIS FOLDER SHOULD CONTAIN ALL THE CONTROLLER CLASSES YOU WILL BE USING FOR
BACKEND

1) CREATE .PY FILE WITH THE NAME OF CONTROLLER (e,i. home.py registration.py)
2) OPEN THE "__init__.py" FILE AND ADD THE NAME OF YOUR MODULE TO THE "__all__"
   ARRAY VARAIBLE 
   